Yes, yes. They troubled
Me and tortured Me.

00:11:41.169 --> 00:11:47.069
They put Me on ice and all, they gave Me
electric shocks.  All of them know all about it.

00:11:50.424 --> 00:11:54.874
Horrible. They think they have a
right, you see to possess somebody.

00:11:54.874 --> 00:11:58.624
This is plundering, this is plundering. Go
to somebody’s country, take away everything,

00:11:58.641 --> 00:12:02.304
plunder that person
and become the king?

00:12:04.744 --> 00:12:07.244
Pirates, I tell you

00:12:16.654 --> 00:12:19.154
Terrible thing they have done.

00:12:19.154 --> 00:12:28.309
But this killing people! Now, in Dhaka, there were
people who used to make beautiful ‘malmal’ , you see.

00:12:28.328 --> 00:12:30.828
A kind of a very thin cloth.

00:12:30.828 --> 00:12:33.328
Very beautiful cloth.

00:12:33.328 --> 00:12:36.759
So thin, they used to develop the nails.

00:12:36.824 --> 00:12:41.339
And in there was a little hole they used to
make. And out of that, they used to take out.

00:12:41.339 --> 00:12:53.620
It was a wonderful thing that one whole dhoti
could be put into a small little shell of a …

00:12:53.640 --> 00:12:55.590
Walnut. Walnut

00:12:55.590 --> 00:12:58.090
Walnut.

00:13:00.860 --> 00:13:05.390
The whole dhoti could
be put inside a walnut.

00:13:05.420 --> 00:13:12.974
And they killed them. All of them, they cut
their thumbs you see, they cut their thumbs.

00:13:12.994 --> 00:13:15.494
So jealous.

