Because the mills of Manchester
sell that cloth there.

00:13:19.844 --> 00:13:24.246
I mean, you cannot compete with
Manchester, because that was…this thing.

00:13:24.246 --> 00:13:30.586
But just an idea. It’s not that… you see, all of them. It's not English, the French, wherever they went, horrible.

00:13:31.352 --> 00:13:33.852
French have ruined so many people.

00:13:33.852 --> 00:13:38.772
Now, this Sierra Leone
where these people went.

00:13:39.369 --> 00:13:48.007
Actually, there are Australians working, but there
are the people who are there, are French, I think.

00:13:48.017 --> 00:13:53.397
The people who are ruling that place is
French. They are so cruel to these people,

00:13:53.430 --> 00:13:55.930
that they have taken to Sahaja Yoga now.

00:13:58.578 --> 00:14:01.078
They’re extremely cruel.

00:14:01.078 --> 00:14:03.578
It’s there all the way
through that part of Africa.

00:14:07.468 --> 00:14:09.968
Portuguese were such
cruel people I tell you.

00:14:10.888 --> 00:14:14.168
Horrible.  Now they have become very poor.

00:14:14.208 --> 00:14:22.419
But all this white skin had that idea of aggressing
others, of plundering others, and sort of ruling everyone.

00:14:22.439 --> 00:14:24.299
Spanish.

00:14:24.299 --> 00:14:29.039
Spaniards are also bad. The whole of
America is covered by these Spaniards.

00:14:30.212 --> 00:14:32.712
I mean, they didn’t kill us so
much, the English, I must say,

00:14:32.712 --> 00:14:37.198
the way they were killed by these
Spaniards for no reason at all.

