And the reason is money again, because they want to get them out of the forests so that they can go in and take the land.

00:15:28.371 --> 00:15:30.871
So they have safaris.

00:15:34.978 --> 00:15:40.118
And you know who, the
nation that goes the most?

00:15:40.168 --> 00:15:41.698
The Germans.

00:15:41.746 --> 00:15:43.446
Oh!

00:15:49.479 --> 00:15:53.426
Germans are very cunning. Now
they are all settled down there.

00:15:53.457 --> 00:16:01.823
This Argentina – that was the only time
I was happy that Argentina was defeated.

00:16:01.823 --> 00:16:04.113
Because all the Germans are there.

00:16:04.113 --> 00:16:07.683
They are teaching them all these things.
They are the ones who started the war.

