having goose steps, these Argentineans?”

00:16:25.959 --> 00:16:29.429
He was also surprised you see
because these only Germans do.

00:16:30.319 --> 00:16:34.300
So when we asked them, they were shocked and
they said, “We have some German teachers.”

00:16:34.312 --> 00:16:39.679
But all Germans who have run away from
the wartime are settled in Argentina.

00:16:39.679 --> 00:16:42.179
And they had big arrangements
to destroy the whole world.

00:16:42.179 --> 00:16:47.019
So this has shattered; that’s the only point where
the British have done something very sensible.

00:16:47.015 --> 00:16:53.081
Maybe I was in England –   very great –
that they have finished those Germans.

00:16:53.081 --> 00:16:55.581
Though it has caused them a
lot of problems, no doubt.

00:16:55.581 --> 00:16:59.525
But that was a sensible thing to do.
Because so many Germans have ruined

00:16:59.573 --> 00:17:02.073
– already building all kinds of things there.

00:17:04.203 --> 00:17:08.133
In Paraguay, just north of there
too, there’s a lot of Germans.

