I mean she is a small country, now come down to your level and don’t tell people that, “We are British, British, British.”

01:12:42.578 --> 01:12:45.078
And all the money is drained off, you see.

01:12:45.078 --> 01:12:48.316
It’s so much trouble to these people, you know.

01:12:48.332 --> 01:12:52.463
Young people are really become
