01:12:52.473 --> 01:12:58.763
All the money is going to missiles. What
are you going to do with these few missiles?

01:12:58.793 --> 01:13:01.293
Hopefully nothing!

01:13:02.443 --> 01:13:05.969
It’s terrible, terrible the way things are happening there.

01:13:05.989 --> 01:13:08.785
You see, I feel sometimes
that this lady has no heart.

01:13:08.785 --> 01:13:10.965
Like a mother to think about her children.
(British Prime Minister, Margaret Thatcher)

01:13:10.965 --> 01:13:15.655
So many young people are unemployed.
She is not bothered about unemployment.

01:13:15.686 --> 01:13:21.826
How these things come in? Because
of unemployment: drugs or anything.

01:13:21.855 --> 01:13:27.412
They have nothing to do poor things, what can they
do? What is their future? She is not bothered

01:13:31.162 --> 01:13:36.170
And now what she’s done? She has
done, is open the, you see, the market.

01:13:36.170 --> 01:13:42.410
This whole thing is open now. Anybody can go
and this bull and this stuff has started there.

