So, yesterday the thing has gone up.

01:13:57.462 --> 01:14:00.934
The pound is up, alright.  But what’s the use?

01:14:04.192 --> 01:14:08.035
The pound has gone up but it’s no
good to you if you haven’t got any.

01:14:08.785 --> 01:14:11.285
It is artificially. It is not really.

01:14:11.285 --> 01:14:15.205
Because she has allowed people to take
their loans, as much as they want.

01:14:15.205 --> 01:14:17.705
Then another thing she has done; a very dangerous thing

01:14:17.705 --> 01:14:29.200
that whatever is the income out of the factories, she wants
to distribute them as bonuses to all the shareholders.

01:14:29.244 --> 01:14:32.792
So the factories will become
tomorrow very weak also.

01:14:33.828 --> 01:14:41.342
All money, all earnings are going to the
people. Just to have cheap popularity.

01:14:41.372 --> 01:14:45.919
Once all the money is wasted and frittered
away like this, what will happen?

01:14:45.955 --> 01:14:49.539
Even if they have more money, what
will they do? They will just drink.

01:14:54.432 --> 01:14:59.533
People are just buying things because they are getting
loans and loans. Everybody is getting a loan there.

01:14:59.533 --> 01:15:04.102
They are very anxious to give loans. And
because of that, the pound has gone up.

01:15:05.849 --> 01:15:08.349
It is a very artificial way.

01:15:08.349 --> 01:15:09.865
The same thing was done with Reagan.

01:15:09.872 --> 01:15:14.465
Also, I must say that, in that country they
gave a lot of loans to other countries

01:15:14.465 --> 01:15:16.965
and that’s how they kept up
themselves. But now where are they?

01:15:16.965 --> 01:15:19.465
They cannot raise their
dollar whatever they may try.

01:15:24.635 --> 01:15:29.977
I mean, that’s not… that’s a capitalist country
now, as far as that thing is concerned.

