They are capitalists who are
ruling. And this is not capitalism.

01:15:33.736 --> 01:15:39.644
This is not conservatism. They
are not conserving at all.

01:15:46.610 --> 01:15:49.208
And this country is another mess I see.

01:15:49.230 --> 01:15:52.528
The labour laws are so high up.

01:15:52.528 --> 01:15:58.498
I remember a long time back, my husband used to say that,
“The worst is the labour of Australia.” I said, "Why?"

01:15:58.498 --> 01:16:02.568
“You see, now they are asking wages for bending.

01:16:02.567 --> 01:16:07.579
So now the wages in the whole of our shipping will
go up and we will have problems,” and this and that.

01:16:07.609 --> 01:16:12.050
So now they raised the wages of the
labour. Alright. So now what’s happening?

01:16:12.070 --> 01:16:16.570
Because the labour is so expensive,
you cannot produce anything.

01:16:16.610 --> 01:16:20.560
Because you cannot produce anything,
so you get everything from abroad.

01:16:20.560 --> 01:16:22.610
People are just having their doles:

01:16:22.610 --> 01:16:28.120
no wages, nothing, not working and spending more
for the things they are getting from abroad.

01:16:28.158 --> 01:16:32.330
Everything is imported in this
country.

01:16:32.382 --> 01:16:37.413
Everything, I was shocked. Everything
is imported in this country.

01:16:37.411 --> 01:16:42.992
It’s going to be like Canada,
which is depending on America.

01:16:43.023 --> 01:16:46.322
The same thing is even happening in
the television industry, Mother.

01:16:46.323 --> 01:16:52.192
One of our problems here in Melbourne,
trying to get television on

01:16:52.192 --> 01:16:56.718
particularly television to take
much interest in Your visit

01:16:56.724 --> 01:16:59.224
is they say, “Oh well, all our programs come from Sydney.”

01:16:59.224 --> 01:17:01.724
So everything’s being imported…

01:17:01.724 --> 01:17:02.748
They are what?

01:17:02.748 --> 01:17:04.728
They all come from Sydney.

01:17:04.728 --> 01:17:08.138
All the programs are in Sydney and they
send them down the line to Melbourne.

01:17:08.175 --> 01:17:14.008
It’s the same sort of thing is happening within
Australia. Everything is getting smaller and smaller.

01:17:14.018 --> 01:17:15.078
Not localised.

01:17:15.078 --> 01:17:15.598
No.

01:17:16.338 --> 01:17:22.516
But one thing is there. You may
not have localised, ah, this thing.

01:17:22.545 --> 01:17:28.749
But supposing tomorrow you start getting
everything from England, then what will happen?

01:17:28.751 --> 01:17:32.359
Everybody will have doles sitting at
home seeing the English programmes.

01:17:32.394 --> 01:17:36.074
And then it might only be from
India you might be getting.

01:17:37.540 --> 01:17:41.194
After sometime and importing even that.

01:17:44.893 --> 01:17:50.876
See, we must not keep our children without any work.

01:17:50.896 --> 01:17:53.916
That’s a very dangerous thing.

01:17:53.936 --> 01:17:55.906
That’s a very dangerous thing to do.

01:17:55.936 --> 01:18:00.116
Oh, I have to take that, I am sorry.

01:18:00.136 --> 01:18:05.345
(Hindi) Please get that to eat, what was
brought here just now. Yes, bran, bran.

01:18:05.364 --> 01:18:09.930
I will have to, according  to treatment of Mister…

01:18:09.952 --> 01:18:15.600
I’ll  just take a second to have this. Let Me have
that. This is Mister… yes, I will take that.

